name: NativeLands
0:
”Alexa, ask Native Lands whose native land am I currently on?”
”Alexa, ask Native Lands what indigenous territory does Boston Massachusetts occupy today?”
”Alexa, ask Native Lands where is the Cherokee territory located?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: native lands
des: Native Lands is an educational Alexa skill designed to inform users about indigenous populations and lands. It uses the information from native-land.ca to answer questions about the Native territories in locations around the world.
